{"tid":693203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣再現反智公園設施？驚現冇得搖搖搖板","createTime":"2018-06-07T09:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T09:58:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab27617fe8067be2c65ad88a0317de141ea86ee","tid":693203,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180607173130\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180607173130&h=f211eb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼青衣長發邨公園出現「千奇百趣」，清一式13隻搖搖騎後，青衣一個居屋屋苑近日被網民亦發現一個「變種」搖搖板設施。典型搖搖板本來是靠槓桿原理令兒童可以上下搖擺嬉戲，但該個搖搖板座位下方卻被支架固定，令搖搖板只剩座椅功能，被居民戲稱為「無得搖&hellip;搖板」。東網就為大家拆解搖搖板「變種」原因。<br />\n<br />\n有青衣居民在Facebook專頁「青衣島民」，分享青盛苑內這個奇怪搖搖板，該搖搖板外型與一般搖搖板外形無異，惟兩端座位下方均有支架固定，使其不能像正常搖搖板般上下搖動。 <br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛猜測該「陰陽怪氣」的設施玩法如何。有人認為其「真身」是平衡木，但若當平衡木去玩隨時令人受傷；有人認為只是搖搖板造型的座椅，有人則分析它的確是搖搖板，惟估計座位下因沒有鋪設地墊，怕市民遊玩時將地磚損壞，索性將其固定。<br />\n<br />\n該設施亦激發網民創意：「高科技油壓搖搖板？」、「畀長者重拾童真用，坐咗當玩咗搖搖板！」，有網民嘲諷：「一定係裝置藝術！」 <br />\n<br />\n東網向青盛苑管理處查詢，成功拆解搖搖板變種的原因。青盛苑管理處發言人指，搖搖板位處青盛苑公眾範圍，由於過去深夜時分經常有人聚集及使用，嘈音滋擾居民，法團多年前通過並決定固定該搖搖板「作座位之用」，發言人又指，固定搖搖板後，再沒有收到居民任何反對意見。 <br />\n<br />\n網民有話說 <br />\n<br />\nChiho Chiu：耐人尋味&hellip; <br />\n<br />\nEdmond Tam：唔係上下，係前後搖咁玩㗎！ <br />\n<br />\nFish Yu：其實係可以鍛鍊身體嘅 SIT UP 新方法！ <br />\n<br />\nCarmen Ng：唔係畀人玩，係畀大媽晾衣服。 <br />\n<br />\nWilson Chow 體操鞍馬嚟㗎！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180607173130\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180607173130&h=aa0f42a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長發邨有公園清一式設置13隻搖搖騎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/bkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fbkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001.html&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e980279a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/bkn-20180607170043131-0607_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3142a76b5354ac2f0ba87c600a908eeaf54cf5b2","tid":693203,"uid":61607,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"948d365d573b5809f5373a6cb0d9bc99afe5bbb8","tid":693203,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"而家仲邊有細路玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e299c22c2039808ec88c425d3e63459a7e274d72","tid":693203,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bc14792a858f8b3502506f9246a9dc2753369cc","tid":693203,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:45:27.000Z","msg":"拆撚哂韆鞦真係好反智"},{"pid":"7e8eae73ef5d9b9440902a3937eb7eac4f0cb334","tid":693203,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"好撚野<br />\n真係香港啲廢柴官先諗到呢啲閪野"},{"pid":"2595b5dc9e4d42c9ee50a98ecbbf366baf833525","tid":693203,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"香港人解決問題既方法真係超英趕美 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f7e68ba675916eb4ad2ea8be46cb87ae0ec318","tid":693203,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"青衣同大陸差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c8c41f36b3bbbe192dff4dfccb6b5eb0f4c25b","tid":693203,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dis